                        Rhodium ended the month $950.00 higher at $8,200.00 (+13.10 %) on the JM Base Price. Meanwhile, the inter-dealer rhodium price closed the month at 8,100 $/oz up 1,025 $/oz. Comparatively, palladium is up 8.5%, and platinum is down 3.2%. The 4E PGM Basket Price is worth 2,054.40 USD/oz.          
                                 
                                 
                                 
                        Whilst the rhodium price has increased 76.5% year-to-date, it has increased 14.1% in the past 30 days.
